phrases: TS
Where did those monsters come from?
They did not make it to the fight with the Secrets?
I heard that they held them back for this day.
This day?
Are you telling me they will be deployed to crush a little security company?
A blackout?
Something happened to the power station?
I even disabled the protector just to record it from TV...
What are you talking about?
They added digital content to the broadcast that did not make it to the official release!
Huh?
You do not have to understand.
Just go and ask what is going on.
Ask your Papa.
Not over it yet?
I thought we were friends.
I have decided to always speak out my mind.
This is an announcement by the security department regarding the earlier blackout.
Nothing went faulty?!
Our power provider terminated our contract
and cut off the power supply.
They terminated the contract?
What about our own generators?
The provider was supposed to be only a backup!
The generators have been stopped since yesterday for an emergency examination.
Orders from above.
Above?
You mean the actual parent company?
The Big Blue World?
Cristophe, what is going on?!
Explain to me what is going on with the people above us!
Sorry, I am still jetlagged...
Just give me a few more minutes...
Hey, Blanc!
Hey!
Let me confirm the conditions once again.
Very well.
The precondition is that in the case of my death,
my daughter, Fleur Blanc, will inherit this contract.
Did something happen to the president?
It seems things are not going too smoothly with the big ones.
Big ones?
When Cristophe learned that there is a way to stop Scub Bursts,
he set up an international rescue team right away.
But he needed an enormous amount of funding, so he used an American PR company's help.
Hey, Fleur!
I heard you successfully activated your Third Engine.
That is amazing!
Is it our fault?
Is it because Elena and I brought Ao back
the Americans and the Big Blue World are making a fuss?
Fleur, to be honest, that is definitely part of the reason.
So it is my fault then!
Then you should just punish us.
You do not need to be so protective just because I am your daughter.
Yeah, I have been protective of you this entire time.
When you kept saying you wanted to pilot an IFO,
I did not allow it until we had enough data to ensure your safety.
But I never stopped you from becoming a pilot.
I wanted you to be proud of your life.
Oh, right!
The company hereby stops eliminating Secrets.
What?
Starting from today, Generation Bleu will focus on suppressing the growth of the Scub Coral.
Based on the earlier UN decision,
the Big Blue World apologizes for Generation Bleu's actions of international hostility.
We have advised President Cristophe Blanc to restructure the company.
Based on our stake in the company, this is an official announcement of the cessation of business.
But your company has controlled Generation Bleu up until now.
Of course.
I have personally been dispatched to oversee them and we paid great heed to compliance.
But President Blanc wantonly took control of the Quartz and used it as a weapon.
And the buddies quarreled.
Now our country has
What is wrong?!
You are going to pretend to be asleep?
Could you at least ask for an appointment before showing up?
What are you going to do?
We should get rid of this terrorist already!
I see you are in a bad mood again.
Nothing happens.
The Plant Corals are reactivated all around the world.
But the Secrets will not show up.
Stuff like that happens.
It is that cannon!
Nirvash's cannon drives the world to chaos and destruction!
But Secrets should be
Quiet.
Listen, Truth.
I am talking to you.
Is that you, Secret?
Let me answer your question.
We are holding back our attacks for now.
Why?
Generation Bleu is becoming the enemy of the world!
That cannon causes chaos, so now would be
Remember, Truth.
What was our goal again?
Order, not chaos.
Our?
You are a Secret as well, are not you?
Or have you forgotten?
What is wrong, Truth?
What are you saying?!
That is ridiculous!
You cannot defeat a Secret.
Naru...
Naru...
The Allied Forces do not know what to do about us.
They want to protect the Scub Coral too.
I did not ask you about that!
Truth, you are a Secret.
I have seen you in the Scub Coral.
Ten years ago on Okinawa, during the greatest Scub Burst that happened in history.
The Secret that emerged there was powerful.
But when the Quartz was taken away, the Secret lost its purpose.
To be accepted into this world, he then took on a human form.
That is me?
And Johansson found me?
But you gave me wings.
You told me what I should do.
You told me to change the world.
By becoming one with the Scub Coral,
humans will be free and have limitless powers
Truth, you are not just a Secret.
You are the same as me.
Arata Naru...
I guided you, thinking that I could destroy the world using Secrets and the Scub Coral.
But...
You are the one who is actually guiding the way?
Ao could not have gotten that power without you.
The Firecracker...
Another one of my forms.
I can dictate the flow of electrons.
Is that a Secret power too?
Even if we cannot take all of the personnel on board,
at least the IFO teams could stay here.
This has always been a safety arc in case something happens on the ground,
so there should not be a problem.
Ao and the others are moving here?
It might come down to that.
But what next?
The president says we will not fight the Secrets anymore.
We must avoid unnecessary conflicts
Mama, we are on a collision course with a satellite.
Calculate an evasion course right away.
It is impossible.
Multiple satellites have crashed into each other and created a cloud of debris.
We are entering a debris storm.
A large number of satellites belonging to both the Allied Forces and the Americans have been destroyed.
They are most likely attacked by Generation Bleu satellites.
As soldiers of the Allied Forces, we are going to siege their headquarters!
Maggie Kwan, how are you feeling?
I am feeling fine, sir.
Sir, the Generation Bleu IFO pilots are those kids, am I correct?
Yeah.
Are we fighting them?
Using the reason that only children can pilot IFOs,
Generation
Bleu may have mistreated those children.
Generation
Bleu may have mistreated those children.
We want to bring them under the Allied Force's protection.
I agree with that plan, sir.
The president will not take any actions, so I
What are you doing?
I am uninstalling the battle assist program.
You are uninstalling Georg?
What will happen if he is gone?
Both the Triton and the IFOs require great movement precision and weapon controls.
In other words, they are useless without Georg.
Do not worry, I am reverting to an earlier version.
It is just a temporary downgrade.
Why would you do that?
To get rid of the virus you brought in.
You mean the Secret?
Yeah.
In Japan, you connected the Secret to Georg.
At that moment, every instance of Georg was activated.
This Georg is a different program because it contains the Secret's consciousness.
So there is no turning back if something goes wrong during a battle, huh?
Is that your decision?
Or did someone from above tell you do that?
It is the same either way!
If they find out we have been infiltrated by a Secret,
we would never be able to negotiate with the Allied Forces!
The Big Blue World abandoned us!
What else do you want to do?!
You cannot say that for sure.
I want to show the company that Generation Bleu is useful.
That is why I must eliminate all dangers.
Dangers?
Is it dangerous to talk with a Secret?
We are founded to fight against Secrets.
That was the only thing that kept this organization going!
Then what about Ivica?
Can you tell him to keep fighting?
That has nothing to do with this.
Yes, it does!
This is not about the company!
I am asking about you!
Here they come.
The Poseidon was shot down.
They will pay for that.
Is what I am hearing about the Poseidon true?
I do not know.
But they will pay.
Compliant to the UN decision, the Allied Forces shall seize all the Quartz that Generation Bleu holds,
as well as the weapon of mass destruction that is suspected to use them.
We are going to forbid their usage of IFOs and other FPs.
Generation Bleu has ceased operating as a company.
All unrequired personnel are ordered to leave the headquarters.
Ao, where is the cannon?
It is locked away underground.
There always seem to be stuff hidden under bases.
Stuff like this.
You do not want to fire it?
You would not understand even if I explained.
Nope, I understand.
Elena?
If you fire that cannon, both Secrets and the Scub Coral will disappear.
The world will change.
That is my world.
Elena?
I will be frank.
I am not a human from this world.
You and your manga references.
It is the opposite, Fleur.
I am not really that into manga.
It is just that what I have lived through seems like a manga.
I can only believe what is impossible.
What do you mean?
I am from another world.
I want to return there.
Ao, you are going to take me with you, right?
Why me?
Because Eureka brought me here.
Hey, you kids
Sorry.
The IFOs will not be launching.
The Poseidon is all right then?
No, Georg has been erased from the IFOs.
We are reinstalling an old version now,
but it will take about an hour to set up all the user data.
But... what if they launch an attack on us?
Sorry for barging in on you.
It is nothing.
But hey, you are okay with Ao being there?
I am not!
Papa?
Papa, what are you doing here?
Keep this a secret from everyone.
Fleur, get ready to escape with me.
Generation
Bleu is done for, but the two of us can still run away.
Wait for me.
How should I say this... there is no doubt he is your dad.
He plans to abandon the company just to protect you.
It is amazing.
Launching all IFOs!
Activate defenses.
Where is Cristophe?!
Fleur, let us get inside the Triton.
It will be safer inside even if it cannot fly.
Ao, come with me!
There is still power here.
Fleur?
Where is Papa?
I mean, the President?
He said he is going to move the Quartz Gun.
He is inside.
Move the cannon?
President!
Fleur...
Too bad.
My Papa is stupid, but he knows me more than anyone else does.
He knows very well that I would rather die
than leave Ao, Elena, and Alleluia to run away with him.
Truth!
Fukai
Ao, what are you doing here?
Truth...
You cannot have the cannon!
That is the only connection I have between Mom and I!
It is not a weapon!
I will not let you make it a weapon!
Shut up!
With this pile of Quartz, I will change the
Are you two all right?
Papa?
Ao, take care of Fleur!
President?
Generation
Bleu will be no more today.
But you still have something you must do.
You must correct our mistake.
Mistake?
What mistake?
The Secrets may not be our enemy.
The Scub Coral may actually be the invader of this world.
There are people infected by the Scub Coral all around the world...
Like Naru...
It is not so easy for adults to correct their mistakes.
We called the Secrets evil, so we cannot go back on that.
But you...
You can find out what is right!
So...
Papa?
Papa!
Nirvash should be able to fly without Georg.
Fly, Ao, Fleur!
The sky is wide open!
What are you thinking?
Do you want to fight me alone?
Truth, I have read Johansson's book too.
I have a theory.
Are not you a Secret who lost his memories?
You are going on about that as well?!
Secrets because a huge explosion when they come into contact with Quartz.
You are no exception either.
What?
Most of the Quartz have been absorbed into the Quartz Gun.
But those we collected in the past few days are kept here.
No way...
Wait!
Confluence explosion.
Papa!
